OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FThe King and Queen will mark the 100th
OL,7,Fanniversary of Queen Elizabeth II with
OL,8,Fthose born in the same year.
OL,10,FThe Royal Family have set out some of
OL,11,Fthe ways they will celebrate the life
OL,12,Fof the late Queen, who would have
OL,13,Fbecome 100 years old this year, having
OL,14,Fbeen born on 21 April 1926.
OL,16,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla have
OL,17,Finvited other centenarians to
OL,18,FBuckingham Palace so they can receive
OL,19,Ftheir centenary birthday cards from
OL,20,Fthe monarch in person.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
