CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775902013
OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FThe Royal Collection Trust has put
OL,7,Ftogether items of her clothing from
OL,8,Fher christening robe to the outfit she
OL,9,Fchose for her last ever balcony
OL,10,Fappearance at Buckingham Palace in
OL,11,F2022.
OL,13,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla will
OL,14,Falso see the wedding dress that the
OL,15,Fthen Princess Elizabeth wore in
OL,16,FNovember 1947 at Westminster Abbey
OL,17,Fwhen she married Prince Philip of
OL,18,FGreece and Denmark.
OL,20,FIn total, there are 300 items on
OL,21,Fdisplay, many for the first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
