OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FPlans are still underway for a
OL,7,Fpermanent memorial to Britain's
OL,8,Flongest-serving monarch.
OL,10,FIt will be built in St James Park,
OL,11,Fright next to The Mall and opposite
OL,12,FBuckingham Palace, which was the late
OL,13,FQueen's official office and residence
OL,14,Ffor the entire 70 years of her reign.
OL,16,FOn April 20, the Prime Minister will
OL,17,Fjoin King Charles and Queen Camilla at
OL,18,Fthe British Museum as they are shown
OL,19,Fthe final design for the national
OL,20,Fmemorial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
