PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775902013
OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FIt will include a replacement bridge
OL,7,Facross the St James' Park lake
OL,8,Finspired by Elizabeth's wedding tiara
OL,9,Fin 1947 and a new gate to remember her
OL,10,Fdevoted husband and consort, Prince
OL,11,FPhilip.
OL,13,FThere will also be a statue or other
OL,14,F'figurative sculpture' which will be
OL,15,Fpositioned right next to The Mall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
