OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FDesigned by a team led by the
OL,7,Farchitect, Lord Norman Foster, the
OL,8,FQueen Elizabeth Memorial will be the
OL,9,Fnation's enduring tribute to Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth, whose reign began in 1952
OL,11,Fand ended in 2022.
OL,13,FOne of the late Queen's former Private
OL,14,FSecretaries, Lord Robin Janvrin, has
OL,15,Fchaired the committee which chose the
OL,16,Ffinal design and will unveil it to the
OL,17,FKing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
