OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775902013
OL,3,CEvents unveiled to mark 100 years
OL,4,Csince the birth of Queen Elizabeth II
OL,6,FLord Janvrin previously spoke to the
OL,7,FTalking Royals podcast about the
OL,8,Fproject, which involved choosing a
OL,9,Fdesign from a range of submissions
OL,10,Fwhich best reflected her contribution
OL,11,Fto the nation over seven decades.
OL,13,FThe late Queen's only daughter,
OL,14,FPrincess Anne, will also officially
OL,15,Fopen the Queen Elizabeth II Garden, a
OL,16,Fnew twoacre space in Regent's Park.
